date: Reviewed in the United States on June 11, 2022
content: I wish I could rate this zero stars, but one star will just have to do. They say this phone case “protects” but it doesn’t, it’s just for show. The case is cheaply-made, it’s just a clear case with a glittery paper glued unto it, so you can remove it anytime or even make this case at home yourself! When my phone fell, it broke on impact (as seen in the attachments above), and that was only from one fall. Think twice before buying this garbage. You’re better off buying a better quality clear phone case and DIYing it, just getting a plain but sturdy case, or purchasing one that is guaranteed to work.
